article_title: No Children Injured After Daycare Van Collides With Car In Spen - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
No children was injured after a daycare van collided with a car in Spencer, Oklahoma, Monday morning.

According to authorities, crews responded to the scene of the crash at N.E. 36th and Douglas.

Four children and one adult were in the van at the time of the collision. They were not injured.

One person in the other car was transported to the hospital to be treated for non-life-threatening injuries.
